text:
How did you guys enjoy watching me play 3 characters? It's not easy making a single person act in 3 parts and make it look this smooth - for which a huge thanks needs to go to Rohit, Ash & Tanya for burning their brains in the process.

The forces behind every part of the video - Neha, Tash, Sukh & both the Harmans as well as the hardworking Sony gang - Jaggi, Diya, Ashish & Shreya also need to be thanked for making this happen.

Hope you guys enjoy vibing to the track and playing it till tennis balls start falling out your ears ;) Make sure you share it with your peeps!
